  - kind: 2
    value: "--8. Add a UNIQUE constraint on CourseName.\r

      \r

      ALTER TABLE Courses \r

      ADD CONSTRAINT uni_course_name UNIQUE (COURSE_NAME);"
    languageId: oracle-sql
  - kind: 2
    value: SELECT * FROM COURSES;
    languageId: oracle-sql
  - kind: 2
    value: "--9. Write SQL to insert a course without specifying CreditHours.\r

      \r

      INSERT INTO Courses (COURSE_ID, COURSE_NAME, DEPARTMENT_ID) VALUES(4,
      'OS', 3);"
    languageId: oracle-sql
  - kind: 2
    value: "--10. Add a FOREIGN KEY in Enrollments using ALTER TABLE\r

      \r

      ALTER TABLE Enrollment\r

      ADD CONSTRAINT fk_student_id\r

      FOREIGN KEY (STUDENT_ID) REFERENCES Students(STUDENT_ID);"
    languageId: oracle-sql
  - kind: 2
    value: "ALTER TABLE Courses\r

      RENAME COLUMN COURSE_NAME to SYLLABUS_NAME;"
    languageId: oracle-sql
